name: Half circle to the mortal World
description:
My first digital artwork on HEN was created in liqufy mode in photoshop with motion video finishing.
inspired by the restlessness of the world that rotates in place of 24-hour life, the technology that leads to the verse, everything wants to be instant, rotates quickly according to its respective portions, will be stable if it is run but will reap disaster if it does not circle in its place in this universe.
